<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Desirous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Desirous,</orth> wishing for, longing after; followed by <cit><quote>of:</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.8.44" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 8, 44</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 1, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.122" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 122</bibl>. By an inf.: <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.213" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 213</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.171" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 171</bibl>. By <emph>should</emph>: <cit><quote>my niece is d. you should enter,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.83" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 1, 83</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>